{"tid":602203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南生圍再起火 蕉樹冒煙消防撲救","createTime":"2018-03-23T00:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T08:14:25.000Z","uid":74778,"like":466,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"940beb206569b730416192349822ec9179ef502c","tid":602203,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T00:30:17.000Z","msg":"南生圍接連發生火警，事件經已引起本港廣泛關注。但僅僅一星期，今晨又再有蕉樹起火，消防員接報到場。在今晨10時半左右，南生圍蠔洲路蕉樹起火，火場面積約10乘3米，事發位置與對上一次火警有一段距離。消防出動一條喉及派出一隊煙帽隊灌救，到場後射水撲救半小時左右，成功將火救熄，調查後相信火警原因無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n南生圍本月初連續兩日發生山火，燒毀大面積的蘆葦叢。有市民更在南生圍其中一個火頭附近，發現一個懷疑載有機油白色塑膠桶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/082330_48ca44e9cf7f7dcfaaec4f624341e1af.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F082330_48ca44e9cf7f7dcfaaec4f624341e1af.png&h=bc4091dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1171062/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1171062%2F&d=pa0BUD9RP%2FDpcUUiG2NN2zCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=5b23d882\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1171062/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>係咪d新聞愈黎愈短，愈黎愈唔洗重視<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母臭閪<br />\n<br />\n兩個禮拜咁放火都可以無事，係咪癡撚左線<br />\n<br />\n警察係咪已經唔撚捉？！<br />\n<br />\n唔撚好又講d 阿sir做野唔洗我教<br />\n<br />\n唔洗教就不如做撚返d野黎睇下<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母，放火放左2星期，乜鳩都唔做，淨係搵火水桶同救火，<br />\n<br />\n個臭閪政府粒聲唔出，形同默許<br />\n<br />\n官商都係仆街陷家剷<br />\n<br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"67da519ffff22cab8a06e8775688e81fe3b2be76","tid":602203,"uid":35430,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T00:31:30.000Z","msg":"無可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b614496a5858992484c2124233208cfcd9b32e6b","tid":602203,"uid":174084,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T00:36:36.000Z","msg":"邊個出糧俾警察?<br />\n<br />\n交稅既人<br />\n<br />\n李生呀~<br />\n<br />\n唔同一般窮LUN咩?"},{"pid":"b9293ea44bea2ab2479d30a95749bb4f47753a44","tid":602203,"uid":70846,"like":162,"dislike":3,"score":159,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T00:47:58.000Z","msg":"講真，朱凱迪去左邊，土地正義聯盟班人去左邊，班大愛環境左翼去左邊"},{"pid":"1eb85c85a1356522490a4ef405b690c31e6abbab","tid":602203,"uid":59961,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01:00:40.000Z","msg":"燒到爛都唔會比你起樓架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"190e6a6b099b47e7b39e68b6f2dc7e8926c82661","tid":602203,"uid":48234,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01:00:41.000Z","msg":"有冇雙失青年做志願軍守南生圍?<br />\n見人放火要當場捉佢俾我嚴刑迫供迫出幕後黑手"},{"pid":"3e6d2d8e7061264fd3db23cd1bf8dbd619ab7ec3","tid":602203,"uid":171901,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01:19:51.000Z","msg":"應從佔中查起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf0bdc50032cc092fdb2d53ed655a384879549d","tid":602203,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01:28:44.000Z","msg":"預計會搵個老同揹條罪"},{"pid":"0bccd36abb3ce3c02c3d6b69ecf9250bc5176a18","tid":602203,"uid":23833,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01:29:59.000Z","msg":"陰謀論：起屋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府既野智慧係咁上下"},{"pid":"962f93a04de05e80861b7d13695686d42068e91f","tid":602203,"uid":34223,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01:30:06.000Z","msg":"呀sir要諗點樣殉職 唔得閒查案"},{"pid":"08fe76f8927c886361ec97a26d35affcaa95428c","tid":602203,"uid":23833,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01:30:38.000Z","msg":"正常邊有可能捉唔到放火條友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n擺明有d野"},{"pid":"ee63e10d8ef982e5642e83f99a031f5b9956d3fe","tid":602203,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass